archimate:DataObject.name: CommunicationInteractionResult
archimate:DataObject.documentation: A CommunicationInteractionResult specifies describes the main result which entity (RootEntity) is impacted and for which action (CommunicationInteractionAction) by the CommunicationInteractionItem. For example: - Action: creates for Entity: CustomerProductOrder CO1 - Action: create for Entity: CustomerProblem CP1 - Action: Help for use for Entity: Billys Broadband - Action: explain Entity: Billys Customer Bill
